brief_title: Ischemic Optic Neuropathy Decompression Trial Followup (IONDT Followup)
brief_summary: To follow all patients enrolled in the original Ischemic Optic Neuropathy Decompression Trial (IONDT) to determine (1) the incidence of non-arteritic ischemic optic neuropathy (NAION) in the second eye, (2) changes in visual acuity over time in both the study and second eye, and (3) other aspects of the natural history of NAION.
eligibility_criteria: All living patients from the 420 patients originally enrolled in the IONDT have been asked to participate in the IONDT Followup Study. No new patients are being recruited.
